nalu: Hoʻopilikia i ka hoʻoili ʻana i ka ikehu me ka lawe ʻole ʻana i ka mea
alapine: Ka helu o nā pōʻai nalu e hala ana i kahi kiko i ka manawa i hāʻawi ʻia
l\u014d\u02bbihi nalu: Ka mamao ma waena o ʻelua mau kiko pili o ka nalu
amplitude: ʻO ka hoʻoneʻe kiʻekiʻe loa o kahi kiko mai kona kaulike ma ka nalu
m\u0101m\u0101: ʻO ke ʻano o ka ikehu e holo ana ma ke ʻano he nalu
electromagnetic spectrum: Ka laulā o nā alapine hawewe electromagnetic āpau
uila uila: ʻO ka ʻokoʻa ʻokoʻa ma waena o ʻelua mau kiko i kahi kaapuni
magnetism: ʻO ka ikaika i hana ʻia e nā magnet ma kekahi mau mea
electromagnet: Mākēneki i hana ʻia e ke au uila ma o ka wili
electroscope: Mea ʻike i ka hele ʻana a me ka hōʻailona o ka hoʻouka uila
kaapuni: ʻO ke ala paʻa e hiki ai ke kahe ka uila
mo\u02bbo: Kaapuni me nā ʻāpana a pau i hoʻopili ʻia i ka loop hoʻokahi
kaulike: Kaapuni me nā ʻāpana pili i nā lālā lehulehu
k\u016b\u02bb\u0113: ʻO ke kū'ē i ke kahe ʻana o ke au uila i loko o kahi conductor
kanawai ohm: ʻO ka pilina ma waena o ka uila, ka manawa, a me ke kū'ē (V = IR)
leki\u014d: Mea ʻikea hiki ke nānā a hoʻokaʻawale paha i nā kukuna māmā
aniani: ʻili maʻalahi e hōʻike ana i ka mālamalama
noonoo ana: Ke hoʻihoʻi i hope o ka māmā, kani, a i ʻole nā nalu ʻē aʻe mai kahi ʻili
ka hoohuli ana: Ka piʻo ʻana o ka mālamalama i kona hele ʻana mai kekahi ʻano a i kekahi
optics: Lala o ka physics e a'o ana i ka malamalama a me kona mau waiwai
